	sizes.

2007-07-11  Peter Jones  <pjones@redhat.com>

	* fsset.py (FileSystemSet.setActive): Don't mark partitions on gpt
	as bootable except in the EFI case, because it screws up PARTITION_LVM
	and makes the partition screen go crazy on a reinstall (related to
	#130236 ).

